# L1-6: Double-sided concrete wall — medium propagation + dual transmission
# Front face at x=2, back face at x=2.3 (0.3m thick)
# eps_r=5.24, sigma=0.05 S/m at 3.5GHz
# Validates: medium attenuation alpha, effective refractive index, dual-transmission chain
o wall_front
v 2.0 -50.0 -50.0
v 2.0 50.0 -50.0
v 2.0 50.0 50.0
v 2.0 -50.0 50.0
vn -1.0 0.0 0.0
f 1//1 2//1 3//1
f 1//1 3//1 4//1

o wall_back
v 2.3 -50.0 -50.0
v 2.3 50.0 -50.0
v 2.3 50.0 50.0
v 2.3 -50.0 50.0
vn 1.0 0.0 0.0
f 5//2 7//2 6//2
f 6//2 7//2 8//2
